  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink298-kilavi">talaimakaṟkuk kuṟainērnta tōḻi talaimakaṭk uṇarttiyavaḻi yavaḷ nāṇattiṉāl maṟaittoḻukiyavataṉaik kūṟak kēṭṭa talaimakaṉ colliyatu.</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the hero said as he heard the confidante speak of the way in which the heroine, out of modesty, kept herself hidden, after the confidante, having granted the hero’s request, had made it known to the heroine.        
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink298">
<l>maḻaivara vaṟiyā maññai yālu</l>
<l>maṭukka ṉallū racainaṭaik koṭicci</l>
<l>tāṉem maruḷā ḷāyiṉum</l>
<l>yāntaṉ ṉuḷḷupu maṟantaṟi yēmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>That creeper-like woman with a swaying gait,</l>
        <l>from the good village on the mountainside</l>
        <l>where peacocks dance, knowing the coming of the rains—</l>
        <l>even if she does not grace us,</l>
        <l>thinking of her, we would not know forgetting [her].</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
